{"tid":2133742,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"原來蘋果日報轉緊新系統，我都打個突。 搵嚟搵去都搵唔到名采。","createTime":"2020-07-31T09:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T13:40:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3f53a896af57205cc5b89067f55b6f5bca8953","tid":2133742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"原來蘋果日報轉緊新系統，我都打個突。<br />\n搵嚟搵去都搵唔到名采。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/T2OWLRXSSZC6TKHKPPYXPIWWU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2FT2OWLRXSSZC6TKHKPPYXPIWWU4%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG17np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=c7d7d17a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2FT2OWLRXSSZC6TKHKPPYXPIWWU4%2F&h=f3f65aee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/T2OWLRXSSZC6TKHKPPYXPIWWU4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鋪後路 - 邁 克<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6hU6fdMuoNobPwGeudd4Qfu6y3w=/621x739/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GKZ3AAASWJATZE3NABKQKGC55A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6hU6fdMuoNobPwGeudd4Qfu6y3w%3D%2F621x739%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGKZ3AAASWJATZE3NABKQKGC55A.png&h=c48a2774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》製作部換上新系統，結果整版副刊在網上不見了，搞了幾天尚未恢復正常，據說手機App版沒問題，但該死的App法國不通用，所以最近左鄰右舍發生什麼完全不知道，氣氛有若數月前的家居隔離。先後接獲多位讀者垂詢，換了太平盛世，他們大概不會如此緊張，風聲鶴唳的時候人人都是驚弓之鳥，一見網站失去更新功能，以為封鎖報館的一幕終於惡夢成真，急急向受害人探問究竟。和盤托出後怕他們大失所望──張愛玲早期散文《談跳舞》寫香港大學生涯，「有一次我們宿舍裏來過賊，第二天早上發現了，女孩們興奮地樓上樓下跑，整個的暑假沒有這麼自由快活過。她們擁到我房門口問：『愛玲小姐，你丟了什麼嗎？』充滿了希望，仿佛應該看見空房間」──幻想中《蘋果》專欄作者集體失業的偉大場面成為泡沫，可能令少女們刺激到患上抑鬱症，於是連忙加一句：「暫時冇事，謝謝關心，不過封報遲早會發生，請繼續期盼，終將不會落空的。」<br />\n<br />\n實不相瞞，冇得撈的心理我早準備好了，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8ba43cd8e6a0766092a5f9ee65c3b4bd1c417c0f","tid":2133742,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"唔好睇咁多咸野喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1dc0a9fb80ce2c961ff1e518905fc08736080e","tid":2133742,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:00:50.000Z","msg":"佢啲尊子漫畫可唔可以高清少少<br />\n<br />\n小學開始追睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821c1961242f97d99a04b8499ce408c031ca70d0","tid":2133742,"uid":124382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"早兩日揾極都冇 update, 最多去到27號。"},{"pid":"10ac4906189b89ebbd8185ecc7a575258fdef89c","tid":2133742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"821c1961242f97d99a04b8499ce408c031ca70d0","tid":2133742,"uid":124382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"早兩日揾極都冇 update, 最多去到27號。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:22:05.000Z","msg":"依家都係去到27號"},{"pid":"fad45516715db5b790d6abdc8a79db1d672bebda","tid":2133742,"uid":124382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10ac4906189b89ebbd8185ecc7a575258fdef89c","tid":2133742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"821c1961242f97d99a04b8499ce408c031ca70d0","tid":2133742,"uid":124382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"早兩日揾極都冇 update, 最多去到27號。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:22:05.000Z","msg":"依家都係去到27號"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:40:17.000Z","msg":"全部冇嘢睇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%B7%A6%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%25B1&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG17np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=07de0847\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%